    dc:description "FIGURE 1 A–F. Gongylonema alecturae Mawson, 1942. A, Cephalic end female, lateral view. B, Vulva and vagina, allotype female, ventral view. C, Posterior end male holotype, ventral view. D, Left spicule distal extremity, co-type male, lateral view. E, Right and left spicules and gubernaculum, co-type male, lateral view. F, Posterior extremity female, lateral view. Scale bars: Fig. 1A, 1B–1E = 50 µm, Fig. 1F = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7624103/files/figure.png" ;
